summary:
- incoming post-graduate research student in Public Policy at Hong Kong University of Science and Technology
- research interest in the Chinese policy-making process, in particular in scitech and innovation policy
- multidisciplinary background in International Studies and Data Science
- curious about Computational Social Science and ways to apply data science and NLP to China-focused research.
- recipient of a full stipend from the German Scholarship Foundation (Studienstiftung des Deutschen Volkes), awarded to less than 0.5% of German students.
